SUMMARY:OT [@rafa]
DESCRIPTION:• listed in [2026-03-20 Fri] from Dewey\n• [2026-04-09 Thu] mes
 sages with PAM about getting an "order"\, they\n  asked which (Cooley or B
 aystate)\, and I replied Baystate because\n  they have openings in June wh
 ereas Cooley has 1-year waitlist.\n  Reply said they should reach out to m
 e within 7 days after they\n  receive "order" from PCP (Dewey).\n• Now hav
